code.dws.core

Class DistantSupervised

  • java.lang.Object
    • code.dws.core.DistantSupervised

  •  class DistantSupervised
extends java.lang.Object
    This class takes a random triple from the OIE projects and computes the Baseline for the subject and object. Uses the mapped candidates to predict the type of the predicates.
    Author:
    Arnab Dutta
